overview: HOOKnSHOOT: BodogFIGHT 2007 Women's Tournament  was an MMA event held on November 24, 2007 in Evansville, Indiana, U.S.. Miesha Tate ambitiously entered the BodogFIGHT 2007 Women's Bantamweight Tournament and was knocked out during her second career bout in the semifinals of the same-night tournament. After the loss, she reeled off five consecutive wins, capturing the Freestyle Cage Fighting women's bantamweight title.
title: HOOKnSHOOT: BodogFIGHT 2007 Women's Tournament
